title: The Queen's Gambit Beth's Story Piano Cover
description:
Carlos Rafael Rivera (born 1970) is an American composer based from Guatemala. In 2014, his music score for the movie A Walk Among the Tombstones advanced for Oscar in the Best Original Score category. Carlos also composed music for the Netflix miniseries Godless.

The Queen's Gambit is an American drama television miniseries based on Walter Tevis's 1983 novel of the same name. It was created by Scott Frank and Allan Scott.
